	(text "Ideally AVDD_H would be \nany voltage higher than \n3.3v since the opamp needs\nheadroom of at least 0.1V\nbut it cannot be 5V since\nthis is the highest supply\nand there's no way of passing\nit through an LDO.\n\nMaybe 4.5V."
